### From v0.x to v1.0

```tsx
// Old (v0.x)
import { KatalystProvider } from '@katalyst/react';

<KatalystProvider theme="dark">
  <App />
</KatalystProvider>

// New (v1.0)
import { KatalystApp } from '@katalyst/core';

<KatalystApp theme="dark">
  <App />
</KatalystApp>
```

## Best Practices

1. **Always wrap your app with KatalystApp or KatalystProvider**
2. **Use design tokens instead of hardcoded values**
3. **Leverage TypeScript for better type safety**
4. **Import components individually for better tree shaking**
5. **Use the built-in hooks instead of reinventing functionality**

## API Reference

See the full [API documentation](https://katalyst.dev/docs/api/core) for detailed component and hook APIs.

## Examples

Check out our [example repository](https://github.com/katalyst/examples) for complete application examples using @katalyst/core.

