##  UI Components

### Pre-built Components (50+)
```tsx
import { 
  Button, Card, Input, Badge, Tabs, 
  DataTable, Form, Modal, Toast, 
  Calendar, DatePicker, Select,
  Carousel, Accordion, Timeline
} from '@katalyst/core';

// AI-powered components
import { 
  AIChat, AISearch, AIRecommendations,
  ContentGenerator, CodeAssistant 
} from '@katalyst/ai';

// Commerce components  
import {
  ProductCard, ShoppingCart, Checkout,
  PaymentForm, OrderTracking
} from '@katalyst/commerce';
```

### Design System
- **Themes**: Light, dark, auto, custom
- **Tokens**: Colors, spacing, typography
- **Accessibility**: WCAG 2.1 AAA compliant
- **Responsive**: Mobile-first design
- **Animations**: Framer Motion integration

##  Code Examples

### Basic App
```tsx
import { KatalystApp, Button, Card } from '@katalyst/core';

function App() {
  return (
    <KatalystApp theme="dark" analytics>
      <Card>
        <h1>Welcome to Katalyst</h1>
        <Button variant="primary">Get Started</Button>
      </Card>
    </KatalystApp>
  );
}
```

### AI Integration
```tsx
import { useAI } from '@katalyst/ai';

function AIComponent() {
  const { generate, loading } = useAI();

  const handleGenerate = async () => {
    const response = await generate({
      model: 'llama-4-scout',
      prompt: 'Write a product description',
      maxTokens: 500
    });
    console.log(response);
  };

  return (
    <Button onClick={handleGenerate} loading={loading}>
      Generate Content
    </Button>
  );
}
```

### E-commerce
```tsx
import { ProductGrid, Cart, Checkout } from '@katalyst/commerce';
import { useCart } from '@katalyst/cart';

function Store() {
  const { items, addItem, total } = useCart();

  return (
    <>
      <ProductGrid 
        products={products}
        onAddToCart={addItem}
      />
      <Cart items={items} total={total} />
      <Checkout />
    </>
  );
}
```

